
---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import GitHubPanel from '../components/GitHubPanel.astro';
---

<Layout>

<header class="nav glass">
  <div class="logo">✈︎ MONTEL GRAY</div>

  <nav>
    <a href="#top">Home</a>
    <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
    <a href="#lab">Lab</a>
    <a href="#scope">Scope</a>
    <a href="#profile">Profile</a>
  </nav>

  <a href="https://github.com/teezyyoxo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="resume">GitHub</a>
</header>

<Hero />

<section class="projects" id="projects">

  <div class="title">
    <h2>Project Range</h2>
    <p>A cross-section of tools, interfaces, infrastructure work, and experiments.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid">

    <article class="card glass">
      <h3>GeoShottr</h3>
      <p>A personal take on screenshot metadata automation, connecting images, location context, and workflow tooling.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card glass">
      <h3>Flight Overlay HUD</h3>
      <p>Aviation-flavored real-time UI work, turning live data into readable operational displays.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card glass">
      <h3>HARSharkNGX</h3>
      <p>A work-adjacent HAR analysis dashboard shaped by real HTTP debugging and inspection needs.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="card glass">
      <h3>Homelab Infrastructure</h3>
      <p>Self-hosted services, containers, automation, and the operational glue around them.</p>
    </article>

  </div>

</section>

<GitHubPanel />

<section class="scope" id="scope">
  <div>
    <p class="section-kicker">Scope</p>
    <h2>Not One Lane, A Working Range</h2>
  </div>

  <p>
    Aviation is one influence in the visual style, but the work itself is broader:
    developer utilities, debugging tools, data-driven interfaces, homelab systems,
    automation workflows, and experiments that start as curiosity or day-job
    friction and turn into usable software.
  </p>

  <div class="scope-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>Product Interfaces</strong>
      <span>Dashboards, portfolio experiences, workflow tools, and clean front-end systems.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Infrastructure</strong>
      <span>Docker, Proxmox, self-hosted services, monitoring, and repeatable setups.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Diagnostics</strong>
      <span>HAR analysis, network inspection, metadata workflows, logs, APIs, and tools for understanding systems.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Automation</strong>
      <span>Scripts, integrations, background jobs, and glue code that removes repetitive work.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Creative Experiments</strong>
      <span>Interactive ideas, visual polish, small prototypes, and projects built to learn fast.</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Aviation Systems</strong>
      <span>Flight-sim overlays, telemetry displays, and cockpit-inspired interaction patterns.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="profile" id="profile">
  <div>
    <p class="section-kicker">Profile</p>
    <h2>Personal Builds, Real Problems</h2>
    <p>
      This site is a map of things I make, remix, and refine: hobby projects,
      work-adjacent utilities, experiments, and tools that solve problems I have
      actually run into.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="profile-actions">
    <a href="https://github.com/teezyyoxo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/teezyyoxo?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Repositories</a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/montelgray/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div>
    <h3>Montel Gray</h3>
    <p>Developer • Systems Builder • Aviation Enthusiast</p>
  </div>

  <div class="links">
    <a href="https://github.com/teezyyoxo" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/teezyyoxo?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Repos</a>
    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/montelgray/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
.nav{
  position:fixed;
  top:20px;
  left:50%;
  transform:translateX(-50%);
  width:min(1200px,92%);
  border-radius:18px;
  padding:18px 24px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  z-index:20;
}

.logo{
  font-weight:800;
  letter-spacing:2px;
}

nav{
  display:flex;
  gap:24px;
}

nav a,
.links a{
  text-decoration:none;
  color:var(--muted);
}

.resume{
  text-decoration:none;
  color:white;
  border:1px solid var(--accent);
  padding:12px 18px;
  border-radius:8px;
}

.projects{
  padding:80px 8%;
}

.title{
  margin-bottom:32px;
}

.title p{
  margin-top:10px;
  color:var(--muted);
}

.grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
  gap:24px;
}

.card{
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:28px;
  color:var(--text);
  text-decoration:none;
  transition:border-color 180ms ease, transform 180ms ease;
}

.card:hover{
  border-color:rgba(0,224,184,0.35);
  transform:translateY(-2px);
}

.card p{
  margin-top:14px;
  line-height:1.7;
  color:var(--muted);
}

.scope,
.profile{
  margin:80px 8%;
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:56px 0 0;
}

.section-kicker{
  color:var(--accent);
  font-family:'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size:0.8rem;
  letter-spacing:3px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}

.scope p,
.profile p{
  margin-top:18px;
  color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.8;
  max-width:760px;
}

.scope-grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:18px;
  margin-top:28px;
}

.scope-grid div{
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:8px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  padding:22px;
}

.scope-grid strong,
.scope-grid span{
  display:block;
}

.scope-grid span{
  color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.7;
  margin-top:10px;
}

.profile{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:flex-end;
  gap:32px;
}

.profile-actions{
  display:flex;
  gap:14px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  justify-content:flex-end;
}

.profile-actions a{
  color:var(--accent);
  text-decoration:none;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:8px;
  padding:12px 16px;
}

footer{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  padding:60px 8%;
}

footer p{
  color:var(--muted);
  margin-top:10px;
}

.links{
  display:flex;
  gap:20px;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

  nav{
    display:none;
  }

  footer{
    flex-direction:column;
    gap:24px;
    text-align:center;
  }

  .scope-grid,
  .profile{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
  }

  .scope-grid{
    display:grid;
  }

  .profile{
    align-items:flex-start;
    flex-direction:column;
  }

  .profile-actions{
    justify-content:flex-start;
  }
}
</style>

</Layout>
